    "summary": "The decision, he said during a speech in Kentucky on Wednesday evening, would “substantially reduce the oil prices as we end this threat to America and this threat to the world.”  The confirmation of the emergency oil release did little to calm volatile markets.  Oil prices ended the session more than 4% higher on Wednesday after yet further volatility as the US and Iran showed no signs of lowering tensions.",
